Package: libpopt
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: an API for parsing command-line options
 libpopt provides API functions for parsing command-line options.
 .
 This package provides the shared library libpopt.

Package: libpopt-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: gcc-dev, libpopt (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development headers and libpopt static library
 This package provides libpopt.a, headers and pkgconfig data required
 to build applications, libraries or plugins using the libpopt API.

